(64, '专业介绍篇（4）──计算机程学院', '<p class="p0" style="margin: 0cm 0cm 0pt"><span style="font-size: small"><strong><span style="color: #ff6600; font-family: 宋体; mso-bidi-font-family: Arial">（<span lang="EN-US">4</span>）计算机学院</span></strong></span><span lang="EN-US" style="font-size: 10.5pt; font-family: &quot;Arial&quot;,&quot;sans-serif&quot;"><u1:p></u1:p><o:p></o:p></span></p>\r\n<p class="p0" style="margin: 0cm 0cm 0pt"><span style="font-size: small"><strong><span lang="EN-US" style="color: #ff6600; font-family: 宋体; mso-bidi-font-family: Arial">1</span></strong><strong><span style="color: #ff6600; font-family: 宋体; mso-bidi-font-family: Arial">、计算机科学与技术</span></strong></span><span lang="EN-US" style="font-size: 10.5pt; font-family: &quot;Arial&quot;,&quot;sans-serif&quot;"><u1:p></u1:p><o:p></o:p></span></p>\r\n<p class="p0" style="margin: 0cm 0cm 0pt; text-indent: 20.6pt"><span style="font-size: small"><strong><span style="color: #ff6600; font-family: 宋体; mso-bidi-font-family: Arial">培养目标：</span></strong><font face="宋体"><span style="color: black; mso-bidi-font-family: Arial">本专业培养适应广东经济建设和社会发展需要，德、智、体、美全面发展，掌握计算机科学与技术的基本理论、基本知识和基本方法，具有扎实的专业知识和良好的学科素养，具有创新精神和实践能力，掌握一门外语，具有较强的计算机系统程序设计能力和程序分析能力，能从事计算机软硬件系统的科研、开发、教学和管理的高素质应用型人才。<img height="224" alt="" width="300" align="right" src="/fore_xtw_file/image/news/2010/7/%E6%A0%87%E5%87%86%E7%9A%84%E7%BD%91%E7%90%83%E5%9C%BA%EF%BC%8C%E7%AD%89%E5%BE%85%E7%9D%80%E4%BD%A0%E5%9C%A8%E8%BF%99%E9%87%8C%E6%8C%A5%E6%B4%92%E6%B1%97%E6%B0%B4%EF%BC%81.jpg" /></span></font></span><font face="宋体"><span lang="EN-US" style="font-size: 10.5pt; font-family: &quot;Arial&quot;,&quot;sans-serif&quot;"><o:p></o:p></span></font></p>\r\n<p class="MsoNormal" style="margin: 0cm 0cm 0pt"><font size="3"><span lang="EN-US" style="mso-bidi-font-size: 10.5pt"><font face="Calibri">&nbsp;<b style="mso-bidi-font-weight: normal"><span style="color: #e36c0a; mso-themecolor: accent6; mso-themeshade: 191"><span style="mso-spacerun: yes">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; </span></span></b></font></span><b style="mso-bidi-font-weight: normal"><span style="color: #e36c0a; font-family: 宋体; mso-bidi-font-size: 10.5pt; mso-ascii-font-family: Calibri; mso-ascii-theme-font: minor-latin; mso-fareast-font-family: 宋体; mso-fareast-theme-font: minor-fareast; mso-hansi-font-family: Calibri; mso-hansi-theme-font: minor-latin; mso-themecolor: accent6; mso-themeshade: 191">主要课程：</span></b><span lang="EN-US" style="mso-bidi-font-size: 10.5pt"><font face="Calibri">C</font></span><span style="font-family: 宋体; mso-bidi-font-size: 10.5pt; mso-ascii-font-family: Calibri; mso-ascii-theme-font: minor-latin; mso-fareast-font-family: 宋体; mso-fareast-theme-font: minor-fareast; mso-hansi-font-family: Calibri; mso-hansi-theme-font: minor-latin">语言程序设计、离散数学、数据结构、电工与电子技术、数字逻辑、计算机组成原理、汇编语言、编译原理、操作系统、数据库原理、计算机网络、计算机系统结构、接口与通信、计算机图形学、网络与信息安全、软件工程、嵌入式系统、算法设计与分析等。选修课程有：人工智能、多媒体技术、网络操作系统、面向对象技术、</span><span lang="EN-US" style="mso-bidi-font-size: 10.5pt"><font face="Calibri">Java</font></span><span style="font-family: 宋体; mso-bidi-font-size: 10.5pt; mso-ascii-font-family: Calibri; mso-ascii-theme-font: minor-latin; mso-fareast-font-family: 宋体; mso-fareast-theme-font: minor-fareast; mso-hansi-font-family: Calibri; mso-hansi-theme-font: minor-latin">语言、电子商务、人机交互、分布式与并行处理、计算机控制系统、通信原理、单片机原理、模糊逻辑及应用、数字图像处理等。</span><span lang="EN-US" style="mso-bidi-font-size: 10.5pt"><o:p></o:p></span></font></p>\r\n<p class="MsoNormal" style="margin: 0cm 0cm 0pt; text-indent: 20.65pt; mso-char-indent-count: 1.96"><font size="3"><b style="mso-bidi-font-weight: normal"><span style="color: #e36c0a; font-family: 宋体; mso-bidi-font-size: 10.5pt; mso-ascii-font-family: Calibri; mso-ascii-theme-font: minor-latin; mso-fareast-font-family: 宋体; mso-fareast-theme-font: minor-fareast; mso-hansi-font-family: Calibri; mso-hansi-theme-font: minor-latin; mso-themecolor: accent6; mso-themeshade: 191">就业方向：</span></b><span style="font-family: 宋体; mso-bidi-font-size: 10.5pt; mso-ascii-font-family: Calibri; mso-ascii-theme-font: minor-latin; mso-fareast-font-family: 宋体; mso-fareast-theme-font: minor-fareast; mso-hansi-font-family: Calibri; mso-hansi-theme-font: minor-latin">可在国家机关与事业单位、金融、财税、海关、医疗、商贸等部门从事办公自动化、电子商务、计算机信息管理、计算机网络等的分析、设计、开发、调试、维护等工作，可在机械制造、邮电通信、建筑、轻工、重工、化工等行业从事计算机检测控制、计算机应用、计算机通信、计算机辅助设计、辅助制造、仪器仪表智能化等工作，也可在科研、教学单位从事科研与教学工作。</span><span lang="EN-US" style="mso-bidi-font-size: 10.5pt"><o:p></o:p></span></font></p>\r\n<p class="MsoNormal" style="margin: 0cm 0cm 0pt"><font size="3"><b><span style="color: #ff6600; font-family: 宋体; mso-bidi-font-family: Arial; mso-bidi-font-size: 10.5pt; mso-ascii-font-family: Calibri; mso-ascii-theme-font: minor-latin; mso-fareast-font-family: 宋体; mso-fareast-theme-font: minor-fareast; mso-hansi-font-family: Calibri; mso-hansi-theme-font: minor-latin">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;学生评价：</span></b><span style="color: black; font-family: 宋体; mso-bidi-font-family: Arial; mso-bidi-font-size: 10.5pt; mso-ascii-font-family: Calibri; mso-ascii-theme-font: minor-latin; mso-fareast-font-family: 宋体; mso-fareast-theme-font: minor-fareast; mso-hansi-font-family: Calibri; mso-hansi-theme-font: minor-latin">该专业为广东省名牌专业！</span><span style="font-family: 宋体; mso-bidi-font-family: Arial; mso-bidi-font-size: 10.5pt; mso-ascii-font-family: Arial; mso-fareast-font-family: 宋体; mso-fareast-theme-font: minor-fareast; mso-hansi-font-family: Arial">人类经历三个时代</span><span style="font-family: 宋体; mso-bidi-font-family: Arial; mso-bidi-font-size: 10.5pt; mso-ascii-font-family: Calibri; mso-ascii-theme-font: minor-latin; mso-fareast-font-family: 宋体; mso-fareast-theme-font: minor-fareast; mso-hansi-font-family: Calibri; mso-hansi-theme-font: minor-latin">：</span><span style="font-family: 宋体; mso-bidi-font-family: Arial; mso-bidi-font-size: 10.5pt; mso-ascii-font-family: Arial; mso-fareast-font-family: 宋体; mso-fareast-theme-font: minor-fareast; mso-hansi-font-family: Arial">农业</span><span style="font-family: 宋体; mso-bidi-font-family: Arial; mso-bidi-font-size: 10.5pt; mso-ascii-font-family: Calibri; mso-ascii-theme-font: minor-latin; mso-fareast-font-family: 宋体; mso-fareast-theme-font: minor-fareast; mso-hansi-font-family: Calibri; mso-hansi-theme-font: minor-latin">、</span><span style="font-family: 宋体; mso-bidi-font-family: Arial; mso-bidi-font-size: 10.5pt; mso-ascii-font-family: Arial; mso-fareast-font-family: 宋体; mso-fareast-theme-font: minor-fareast; mso-hansi-font-family: Arial">工</span><span style="font-family: 宋体; mso-bidi-font-family: Arial; mso-bidi-font-size: 10.5pt; mso-ascii-font-family: Calibri; mso-ascii-theme-font: minor-latin; mso-fareast-font-family: 宋体; mso-fareast-theme-font: minor-fareast; mso-hansi-font-family: Calibri; mso-hansi-theme-font: minor-latin">业，</span><span style="font-family: 宋体; mso-bidi-font-family: Arial; mso-bidi-font-size: 10.5pt; mso-ascii-font-family: Arial; mso-fareast-font-family: 宋体; mso-fareast-theme-font: minor-fareast; mso-hansi-font-family: Arial">现在正是信息时代</span><span style="font-family: 宋体; mso-bidi-font-family: Arial; mso-bidi-font-size: 10.5pt; mso-ascii-font-family: Calibri; mso-ascii-theme-font: minor-latin; mso-fareast-font-family: 宋体; mso-fareast-theme-font: minor-fareast; mso-hansi-font-family: Calibri; mso-hansi-theme-font: minor-latin">，</span><span style="font-family: 宋体; mso-bidi-font-family: Arial; mso-bidi-font-size: 10.5pt; mso-ascii-font-family: Arial; mso-fareast-font-family: 宋体; mso-fareast-theme-font: minor-fareast; mso-hansi-font-family: Arial">很有前途</span><span style="font-family: 宋体; mso-bidi-font-family: Arial; mso-bidi-font-size: 10.5pt; mso-ascii-font-family: Calibri; mso-ascii-theme-font: minor-latin; mso-fareast-font-family: 宋体; mso-fareast-theme-font: minor-fareast; mso-hansi-font-family: Calibri; mso-hansi-theme-font: minor-latin">，</span><span style="font-family: 宋体; mso-bidi-font-family: Arial; mso-bidi-font-size: 10.5pt; mso-ascii-font-family: Arial; mso-fareast-font-family: 宋体; mso-fareast-theme-font: minor-fareast; mso-hansi-font-family: Arial">市场需求量也很大</span><span style="font-family: 宋体; mso-bidi-font-family: Arial; mso-bidi-font-size: 10.5pt; mso-ascii-font-family: Calibri; mso-ascii-theme-font: minor-latin; mso-fareast-font-family: 宋体; mso-fareast-theme-font: minor-fareast; mso-hansi-font-family: Calibri; mso-hansi-theme-font: minor-latin">，</span><span style="font-family: 宋体; mso-bidi-font-family: Arial; mso-bidi-font-size: 10.5pt; mso-ascii-font-family: Arial; mso-fareast-font-family: 宋体; mso-fareast-theme-font: minor-fareast; mso-hansi-font-family: Arial">尽管现在开设这科的学校很多</span><span style="font-family: 宋体; mso-bidi-font-family: Arial; mso-bidi-font-size: 10.5pt; mso-ascii-font-family: Calibri; mso-ascii-theme-font: minor-latin; mso-fareast-font-family: 宋体; mso-fareast-theme-font: minor-fareast; mso-hansi-font-family: Calibri; mso-hansi-theme-font: minor-latin">，</span><span style="font-family: 宋体; mso-bidi-font-family: Arial; mso-bidi-font-size: 10.5pt; mso-ascii-font-family: Arial; mso-fareast-font-family: 宋体; mso-fareast-theme-font: minor-fareast; mso-hansi-font-family: Arial">毕业的学生也很多</span><span style="font-family: 宋体; mso-bidi-font-family: Arial; mso-bidi-font-size: 10.5pt; mso-ascii-font-family: Calibri; mso-ascii-theme-font: minor-latin; mso-fareast-font-family: 宋体; mso-fareast-theme-font: minor-fareast; mso-hansi-font-family: Calibri; mso-hansi-theme-font: minor-latin">，</span><span style="font-family: 宋体; mso-bidi-font-family: Arial; mso-bidi-font-size: 10.5pt; mso-ascii-font-family: Arial; mso-fareast-font-family: 宋体; mso-fareast-theme-font: minor-fareast; mso-hansi-font-family: Arial">但真正学得精的人太少</span><span style="font-family: 宋体; mso-bidi-font-family: Arial; mso-bidi-font-size: 10.5pt; mso-ascii-font-family: Calibri; mso-ascii-theme-font: minor-latin; mso-fareast-font-family: 宋体; mso-fareast-theme-font: minor-fareast; mso-hansi-font-family: Calibri; mso-hansi-theme-font: minor-latin">，</span><span style="font-family: 宋体; mso-bidi-font-family: Arial; mso-bidi-font-size: 10.5pt; mso-ascii-font-family: Arial; mso-fareast-font-family: 宋体; mso-fareast-theme-font: minor-fareast; mso-hansi-font-family: Arial">所以很多人说就不了业</span><span style="font-family: 宋体; mso-bidi-font-family: Arial; mso-bidi-font-size: 10.5pt; mso-ascii-font-family: Calibri; mso-ascii-theme-font: minor-latin; mso-fareast-font-family: 宋体; mso-fareast-theme-font: minor-fareast; mso-hansi-font-family: Calibri; mso-hansi-theme-font: minor-latin">，</span><span style="font-family: 宋体; mso-bidi-font-family: Arial; mso-bidi-font-size: 10.5pt; mso-ascii-font-family: Arial; mso-fareast-font-family: 宋体; mso-fareast-theme-font: minor-fareast; mso-hansi-font-family: Arial">实际上市场需要真正有本事的人</span><span style="font-family: 宋体; mso-bidi-font-family: Arial; mso-bidi-font-size: 10.5pt; mso-ascii-font-family: Calibri; mso-ascii-theme-font: minor-latin; mso-fareast-font-family: 宋体; mso-fareast-theme-font: minor-fareast; mso-hansi-font-family: Calibri; mso-hansi-theme-font: minor-latin">！</span></font></p>\r\n<hr />\r\n<p class="MsoNormal" style="margin: 0cm 0cm 0pt">&nbsp;<span style="font-size: small"><strong><span lang="EN-US" style="color: #ff6600; font-family: 宋体; mso-bidi-font-family: Arial">2</span><span style="color: #ff6600; font-family: 宋体; mso-bidi-font-family: Arial">、软件工程</span></strong></span></p>\r\n<p class="p0" style="margin: 0cm 0cm 0pt; text-indent: 20.6pt"><span style="font-size: small"><strong><span style="color: #ff6600; font-family: 宋体; mso-bidi-font-family: Arial">培养目标：</span></strong><font face="宋体"><span style="color: black; mso-bidi-font-family: Arial">本专业培养适应广东经济建设和社会发展需要的，德、智、体、美全面发展，具有扎实的专业理论基础和良好的学科素养，具有创新精神和实践能力，掌握计算机科学基础理论、软件工程专业及应用知识，具有软件开发能力和项目管理的初步经验，具有竞争和团队精神，能从事计算机软件开发、维护和管理的高素质应用型人才。<img height="188" alt="" width="300" align="left" src="/fore_xtw_file/image/news/2010/%E8%B6%B3%E7%90%83%E5%9C%BA.jpg" /></span></font></span><font face="宋体"><span lang="EN-US" style="font-size: 10.5pt; font-family: &quot;Arial&quot;,&quot;sans-serif&quot;"><o:p></o:p></span></font></p>\r\n<p class="MsoNormal" style="margin: 0cm 0cm 0pt"><font size="3"><span lang="EN-US" style="mso-bidi-font-size: 10.5pt"><font face="Calibri">&nbsp;<b style="mso-bidi-font-weight: normal"><span style="color: #e36c0a; mso-themecolor: accent6; mso-themeshade: 191"><span style="mso-spacerun: yes">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; </span></span></b></font></span><b style="mso-bidi-font-weight: normal"><span style="color: #e36c0a; font-family: 宋体; mso-bidi-font-size: 10.5pt; mso-ascii-font-family: Calibri; mso-ascii-theme-font: minor-latin; mso-fareast-font-family: 宋体; mso-fareast-theme-font: minor-fareast; mso-hansi-font-family: Calibri; mso-hansi-theme-font: minor-latin; mso-themecolor: accent6; mso-themeshade: 191">主要课程：</span></b><span style="font-family: 宋体; mso-bidi-font-size: 10.5pt; mso-ascii-font-family: Calibri; mso-ascii-theme-font: minor-latin; mso-fareast-font-family: 宋体; mso-fareast-theme-font: minor-fareast; mso-hansi-font-family: Calibri; mso-hansi-theme-font: minor-latin">线性代数、概率与数理统计、</span><span lang="EN-US" style="mso-bidi-font-size: 10.5pt"><font face="Calibri">C</font></span><span style="font-family: 宋体; mso-bidi-font-size: 10.5pt; mso-ascii-font-family: Calibri; mso-ascii-theme-font: minor-latin; mso-fareast-font-family: 宋体; mso-fareast-theme-font: minor-fareast; mso-hansi-font-family: Calibri; mso-hansi-theme-font: minor-latin">语言程序设计、离散数学、数据结构、电工与电子技术、数字逻辑、计算机组成原理、汇编语言、编译原理、操作系统、数据库原理、计算机网络、计算机系统结构、软件工程、算法设计与分析、软件代码技术开发、计算机图形学等。选修课程有：软件需求分析、软件项目管理、软件质量保证与测试、软件设计与体系结构、嵌入式系统、网络与信息安全、人工智能、多媒体技术、网络操作系统、面向对象技术、</span><span lang="EN-US" style="mso-bidi-font-size: 10.5pt"><font face="Calibri">Java</font></span><span style="font-family: 宋体; mso-bidi-font-size: 10.5pt; mso-ascii-font-family: Calibri; mso-ascii-theme-font: minor-latin; mso-fareast-font-family: 宋体; mso-fareast-theme-font: minor-fareast; mso-hansi-font-family: Calibri; mso-hansi-theme-font: minor-latin">语言、人机交互、团队激励和沟通等。</span><span lang="EN-US" style="mso-bidi-font-size: 10.5pt"><o:p></o:p></span></font></p>\r\n<p class="MsoNormal" style="margin: 0cm 0cm 0pt; text-indent: 20.45pt; mso-char-indent-count: 1.94"><font size="3"><b style="mso-bidi-font-weight: normal"><span style="color: #e36c0a; font-family: 宋体; mso-bidi-font-size: 10.5pt; mso-ascii-font-family: Calibri; mso-ascii-theme-font: minor-latin; mso-fareast-font-family: 宋体; mso-fareast-theme-font: minor-fareast; mso-hansi-font-family: Calibri; mso-hansi-theme-font: minor-latin; mso-themecolor: accent6; mso-themeshade: 191">&nbsp;就业方向：</span></b><span style="font-family: 宋体; mso-bidi-font-size: 10.5pt; mso-ascii-font-family: Calibri; mso-ascii-theme-font: minor-latin; mso-fareast-font-family: 宋体; mso-fareast-theme-font: minor-fareast; mso-hansi-font-family: Calibri; mso-hansi-theme-font: minor-latin">可在国家机关与事业单位、金融、财税、海关、医疗、商贸等部门从事软件工程、办公自动化、电子商务、计算机信息管理、计算机网络软件等的分析、设计、开发、维护等工作，可在政府机关、教育科研部门、企事业单位等从事计算机软件设计、软件评审与测试、软件过程改进与项目管理等工作，也可在科研、教学单位从事科研与教学工作。</span><span lang="EN-US" style="mso-bidi-font-size: 10.5pt"><o:p></o:p></span></font></p>\r\n<p class="MsoNormal" style="margin: 0cm 0cm 0pt; text-indent: 15.4pt; mso-char-indent-count: 1.46"><font size="3"><strong><span style="color: #ff6600; font-family: 宋体; mso-bidi-font-family: Arial; mso-bidi-font-size: 10.5pt; mso-ascii-font-family: Calibri; mso-ascii-theme-font: minor-latin; mso-fareast-font-family: 宋体; mso-fareast-theme-font: minor-fareast; mso-hansi-font-family: Calibri; mso-hansi-theme-font: minor-latin">&nbsp;学生评价：</span></strong><span style="font-family: 宋体; mso-bidi-font-family: Arial; mso-bidi-font-size: 10.5pt; mso-ascii-font-family: Calibri; mso-ascii-theme-font: minor-latin; mso-fareast-font-family: 宋体; mso-fareast-theme-font: minor-fareast; mso-hansi-font-family: Calibri; mso-hansi-theme-font: minor-latin">软件工程人才的就业前景十分看好。未来几年，国内外高层次软件人才将供不应求。毕业生主要在各大软件公司、企事业单位、高等院校、各大研究所、国防等重要部门从事软件设计、开发、应用与研究工作。有数据表明，我国软件出口规模达到</span><span lang="EN-US" style="mso-bidi-font-family: Arial; mso-bidi-font-size: 10.5pt"><font face="Calibri">215</font></span><span style="font-family: 宋体; mso-bidi-font-family: Arial; mso-bidi-font-size: 10.5pt; mso-ascii-font-family: Calibri; mso-ascii-theme-font: minor-latin; mso-fareast-font-family: 宋体; mso-fareast-theme-font: minor-fareast; mso-hansi-font-family: Calibri; mso-hansi-theme-font: minor-latin">亿元，软件从业人员达到</span><span lang="EN-US" style="mso-bidi-font-family: Arial; mso-bidi-font-size: 10.5pt"><font face="Calibri">72</font></span><span style="font-family: 宋体; mso-bidi-font-family: Arial; mso-bidi-font-size: 10.5pt; mso-ascii-font-family: Calibri; mso-ascii-theme-font: minor-latin; mso-fareast-font-family: 宋体; mso-fareast-theme-font: minor-fareast; mso-hansi-font-family: Calibri; mso-hansi-theme-font: minor-latin">万人，在中国十大</span><span lang="EN-US" style="mso-bidi-font-family: Arial; mso-bidi-font-size: 10.5pt"><font face="Calibri">IT</font></span><span style="font-family: 宋体; mso-bidi-font-family: Arial; mso-bidi-font-size: 10.5pt; mso-ascii-font-family: Calibri; mso-ascii-theme-font: minor-latin; mso-fareast-font-family: 宋体; mso-fareast-theme-font: minor-fareast; mso-hansi-font-family: Calibri; mso-hansi-theme-font: minor-latin">职场人气职位中，软件工程师位列第一位，软件工程人才的就业前景十分乐观。</span></font></p>\r\n<hr />\r\n<p class="MsoNormal" style="margin: 0cm 0cm 0pt; text-indent: 15.4pt; mso-char-indent-count: 1.46">&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p class="p0" style="margin: 0cm 0cm 0pt"><span style="font-size: small"><strong><span lang="EN-US" style="color: #ff6600; font-family: 宋体; mso-bidi-font-family: Arial">3</span></strong><strong><span style="color: #ff6600; font-family: 宋体; mso-bidi-font-family: Arial">、网络工程（网络系统开发与管理方向）</span></strong></span><span lang="EN-US" style="font-size: 10.5pt; font-family: &quot;Arial&quot;,&quot;sans-serif&quot;"><u1:p></u1:p><o:p></o:p></span></p>\r\n<p class="p0" style="margin: 0cm 0cm 0pt; text-indent: 25.75pt"><span style="font-size: small"><strong><span style="color: #ff6600; font-family: 宋体; mso-bidi-font-family: Arial">培养目标：</span></strong><font face="宋体"><span style="color: black; mso-bidi-font-family: Arial">本专业培养适应广东经济建设和社会发展需要的，德、智、体、美全面发展，具有扎实的专业理论基础和良好的学科素养，具有创新精神和实践能力，掌握一门外语，较好地掌握网络工程的基本理论、基础知识和基本技能，能运用所学知识与技能去分析和解决计算机网络的实际应用问题，能从事计算机网络系统的科研、开发、教学和管理的高素质应用型人才。<img height="224" alt="" width="300" align="right" src="/fore_xtw_file/image/news/2010/%E7%AF%AE%E7%90%83%E5%9C%BA.jpg" /></span></font></span><font face="宋体"><span lang="EN-US" style="font-size: 10.5pt; font-family: &quot;Arial&quot;,&quot;sans-serif&quot;"><o:p></o:p></span></font></p>\r\n<p class="MsoNormal" style="margin: 0cm 0cm 0pt"><font size="3"><span lang="EN-US" style="mso-bidi-font-size: 10.5pt"><font face="Calibri">&nbsp;<b style="mso-bidi-font-weight: normal"><span style="color: #e36c0a; mso-themecolor: accent6; mso-themeshade: 191"><span style="mso-spacerun: yes">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; &nbsp;</span></span></b></font></span><b style="mso-bidi-font-weight: normal"><span style="color: #e36c0a; font-family: 宋体; mso-bidi-font-size: 10.5pt; mso-ascii-font-family: Calibri; mso-ascii-theme-font: minor-latin; mso-fareast-font-family: 宋体; mso-fareast-theme-font: minor-fareast; mso-hansi-font-family: Calibri; mso-hansi-theme-font: minor-latin; mso-themecolor: accent6; mso-themeshade: 191">主要课程：</span></b><span lang="EN-US" style="mso-bidi-font-size: 10.5pt"><font face="Calibri">C</font></span><span style="font-family: 宋体; mso-bidi-font-size: 10.5pt; mso-ascii-font-family: Calibri; mso-ascii-theme-font: minor-latin; mso-fareast-font-family: 宋体; mso-fareast-theme-font: minor-fareast; mso-hansi-font-family: Calibri; mso-hansi-theme-font: minor-latin">语言程序设计、离散数学、数据结构、电工与电子技术、数字逻辑、计算机组成原理、汇编语言、编译原理、操作系统、数据库原理、计算机网络、计算机系统结构、接口与通信、网络工程设计、计算机图形学、网络与信息安全、软件工程等。选修课程有：计算机组网技术、网络管理与维护、协议分析与编程、嵌入式系统、人工智能、算法设计与分析、多媒体技术、网络操作系统、</span><span lang="EN-US" style="mso-bidi-font-size: 10.5pt"><font face="Calibri">Java</font></span><span style="font-family: 宋体; mso-bidi-font-size: 10.5pt; mso-ascii-font-family: Calibri; mso-ascii-theme-font: minor-latin; mso-fareast-font-family: 宋体; mso-fareast-theme-font: minor-fareast; mso-hansi-font-family: Calibri; mso-hansi-theme-font: minor-latin">语言、电子商务、人机交互、通信原理、</span><span lang="EN-US" style="mso-bidi-font-size: 10.5pt"><font face="Calibri">Web</font></span><span style="font-family: 宋体; mso-bidi-font-size: 10.5pt; mso-ascii-font-family: Calibri; mso-ascii-theme-font: minor-latin; mso-fareast-font-family: 宋体; mso-fareast-theme-font: minor-fareast; mso-hansi-font-family: Calibri; mso-hansi-theme-font: minor-latin">开发技术、现代交换技术等。</span><span lang="EN-US" style="mso-bidi-font-size: 10.5pt"><o:p></o:p></span></font></p>\r\n<p class="MsoNormal" style="margin: 0cm 0cm 0pt; text-indent: 20.65pt; mso-char-indent-count: 1.96"><font size="3"><b style="mso-bidi-font-weight: normal"><span style="color: #e36c0a; font-family: 宋体; mso-bidi-font-size: 10.5pt; mso-ascii-font-family: Calibri; mso-ascii-theme-font: minor-latin; mso-fareast-font-family: 宋体; mso-fareast-theme-font: minor-fareast; mso-hansi-font-family: Calibri; mso-hansi-theme-font: minor-latin; mso-themecolor: accent6; mso-themeshade: 191">&nbsp;就业方向：</span></b><span style="font-family: 宋体; mso-bidi-font-size: 10.5pt; mso-ascii-font-family: Calibri; mso-ascii-theme-font: minor-latin; mso-fareast-font-family: 宋体; mso-fareast-theme-font: minor-fareast; mso-hansi-font-family: Calibri; mso-hansi-theme-font: minor-latin">可在国家机关与事业单位，金融、财税、海关、商业、贸易等部门行业从事网络工程、电子商务、办公自动化、信息管理等的开发、设计、维护工作，可在政府机关、教育科研部门、企事业单位等从事网络系统开发、网络组建、网络管理、网络信息安全、电子商务等工作。也可在科研机构、学校从事科研与教学工作。</span><span lang="EN-US" style="mso-bidi-font-size: 10.5pt"><o:p></o:p></span></font></p>\r\n<p class="MsoNormal" style="margin: 0cm 0cm 0pt; text-indent: 20.65pt; mso-char-indent-count: 1.96"><font size="3"><strong><span style="color: #ff6600; font-family: 宋体; mso-bidi-font-family: Arial; mso-bidi-font-size: 10.5pt; mso-ascii-font-family: Calibri; mso-ascii-theme-font: minor-latin; mso-fareast-font-family: 宋体; mso-fareast-theme-font: minor-fareast; mso-hansi-font-family: Calibri; mso-hansi-theme-font: minor-latin">&nbsp;学生评价：</span></strong><span style="font-family: 宋体; mso-bidi-font-family: Arial; mso-bidi-font-size: 10.5pt; mso-ascii-font-family: Calibri; mso-ascii-theme-font: minor-latin; mso-fareast-font-family: 宋体; mso-fareast-theme-font: minor-fareast; mso-hansi-font-family: Calibri; mso-hansi-theme-font: minor-latin">在当前信息社会，</span><span lang="EN-US" style="mso-bidi-font-family: Arial; mso-bidi-font-size: 10.5pt; mso-ascii-font-family: Calibri; mso-hansi-font-family: Calibri"><font face="Calibri">IT</font></span><span style="font-family: 宋体; mso-bidi-font-family: Arial; mso-bidi-font-size: 10.5pt; mso-ascii-font-family: Calibri; mso-ascii-theme-font: minor-latin; mso-fareast-font-family: 宋体; mso-fareast-theme-font: minor-fareast; mso-hansi-font-family: Calibri; mso-hansi-theme-font: minor-latin">技术发展日新月异，同时也日益渗透到我们的生活、工作、学习、娱乐当中。在我们享受信息化带给我们便利的同时，也对</span><span lang="EN-US" style="mso-bidi-font-family: Arial; mso-bidi-font-size: 10.5pt; mso-ascii-font-family: Calibri; mso-hansi-font-family: Calibri"><font face="Calibri">IT</font></span><span style="font-family: 宋体; mso-bidi-font-family: Arial; mso-bidi-font-size: 10.5pt; mso-ascii-font-family: Calibri; mso-ascii-theme-font: minor-latin; mso-fareast-font-family: 宋体; mso-fareast-theme-font: minor-fareast; mso-hansi-font-family: Calibri; mso-hansi-theme-font: minor-latin">技术充满了向往，对</span><span lang="EN-US" style="mso-bidi-font-family: Arial; mso-bidi-font-size: 10.5pt; mso-ascii-font-family: Calibri; mso-hansi-font-family: Calibri"><font face="Calibri">IT</font></span><span style="font-family: 宋体; mso-bidi-font-family: Arial; mso-bidi-font-size: 10.5pt; mso-ascii-font-family: Calibri; mso-ascii-theme-font: minor-latin; mso-fareast-font-family: 宋体; mso-fareast-theme-font: minor-fareast; mso-hansi-font-family: Calibri; mso-hansi-theme-font: minor-latin">工程师职业更是羡慕！虽然这专业的待遇很好，但是竞争压力很大！只有好好学习，才能使自己能够在当前金融危机和激烈的职场竞争下逆风飞扬！</span></font><span lang="EN-US" style="mso-bidi-font-size: 10.5pt"><u1:p></u1:p><o:p></o:p></span></p>\r\n<p class="p0" style="margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt">&nbsp;</p>', '工大在线', 1, '2010-07-22 16:00:12', 1),
